title: Account bugged?
body: Hey i'm having some issues with my Account, For the past 2 days i have not been able to search for a game and when i do it just says receiving  data from server. I log off and when i try to log back in it won't let me, I asked some friends to see if i was still online and they said i was still in queue when i was on the log in screen. Can anyone hep me?
